description: Danny Arroyo  is with  Dawn Kennington Bejar  and  46 others . I've done this once before and thought it would be fun again, so here you go.  Anyone interested in a holiday gift exchange?! I don't care where you live, you are welcome to join. I need at least 6 ladies to participate in a SECRET SISTER gift exchange. You only have to buy ONE gift valued at at least $10 or more and send it to ONE secret sister, and you will receive 6-36 in return!! SO much fun!! We need some love and light these days!  Let me know if you are interested and I will PM you the information!  ❤  Please don't ask to participate if you're not willing to spend the $10. The holidays are getting closer!! Fun times to get a secret gift in the mail, through the holiday season, as we are all prepping and shopping for those around us.   I just tagged a bunch of people.
